WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.009 --> 00:00:02.690
To filter a list based on a specific value,

1
00:00:03.009 --> 00:00:06.670
mouse over the value itself to reveal the Filter Menu button.

2
00:00:07.010 --> 00:00:10.350
Select Show Matching to display only records with that value,

3
00:00:10.569 --> 00:00:12.789
or Filter Out to exclude them from the list.

4
00:00:14.170 --> 00:00:16.969
The filter condition is added to the Filter Panel

5
00:00:17.129 --> 00:00:19.629
where it can be reviewed or modified if needed.
